 "blurb": "Feral Cat is the highest-skill melee rotation in TBC: powershifting out of form every few seconds for Wolfshead energy, Mangle and Rip upkeep in between, and an instant off-tank switch nobody else offers. The phase lists double as your bear offset — one gear track, two jobs. This Phase 1 snapshot aggregates 334 top DPS parses from Karazhan, Gruul's Lair and Magtheridon; the highest-consensus pick is Wolfshead Helm at 95% usage.",
